    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >连续加班第27天的深夜，你回到空无一人的房间，习惯性地打开电脑。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本能般地把一个看起来挺感兴趣的游戏加入了库中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是第1000个。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如今的你已经没了少年时打游戏的心境，也没有了一起打游戏的朋友。躺在椅子上沉沉睡去，醒来却到了另一个世界......</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255500/extras/7f1c87189b59da8b760edb0e2a6c1c1b.avif?t=1770360080\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255500/extras_big/7f1c87189b59da8b760edb0e2a6c1c1b.avif?t=1770360080 width=800 height=394 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255500/extras/268cb1982b7793a0a88c92650ecf5b9c.webp?t=1770360080\" width=616 height=62 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7个可操作角色，不同手感、不同能力、不同性格的角色和你一起冒险，共同通关这款游戏，探索这个世界的真相，回到现实。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完全不同的动作模组，局内的动作升级，每个角色都会给你带来完全不一样的体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255500/extras/1df398dfdafa56ebf8692cc74352b9a1.avif?t=1770360080\" width=616 height=587 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255500/extras/82f2d477d9548bb4903c7548c26644b7.webp?t=1770360080\" width=616 height=62 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >9大流派属性、90余种不同效果的非数值Buff，区别于传统肉鸽的构筑系统，完全自由安装组合的Buff链，相互触发联动的Buff，让你每一局都能随心所欲地体验多样的战斗。 <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255500/extras/f0c527105a1ec6d15ce0cf1a97d4dd20.poster.avif?t=1770360080\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255500/extras/f0c527105a1ec6d15ce0cf1a97d4dd20.webm?t=1770360080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>在紧张刺激的战斗中通过自定义操作触发不同的Buff，运用你手中的Buff运筹帷幄，战胜敌人！<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255500/extras/9d74da29b20412e731c518950c7dd005.poster.avif?t=1770360080\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255500/extras/9d74da29b20412e731c518950c7dd005.webm?t=1770360080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255500/extras/382459a02f78c0d1254c81ea91d025c4.webp?t=1770360080\" width=616 height=62 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4大风格迥异的大关，总共16个Boss，在收集了足够的能力后，格挡！闪避！进攻！纯粹的战斗爽！与之一战！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255500/extras/c411ab8fea65788687997ece98a309cb.poster.avif?t=1770360080\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255500/extras/c411ab8fea65788687997ece98a309cb.webm?t=1770360080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255500/extras/6fe7e4eb4175c666ade5f5e88d59a175.webp?t=1770360080\" width=616 height=62 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50种不同的装备，收集特殊的隐藏词条，对局内Buff产生实质影响。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >装扮你的角色，更快速地解决敌人！<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255500/extras/f59e12011bea606d28a9281b6d21eae5.poster.avif?t=1770360080\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255500/extras/f59e12011bea606d28a9281b6d21eae5.webm?t=1770360080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
